tive\\n  ? (searchData?.checkpoints ?? [])\\n  : allCheckpoints;\\n```\\n\\nAlso add a loading indicator when search is in progress, and update the empty state to show \\\"No results for {query}\\\".\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n1. Set `TURBOPUFFER_API_KEY` as a wrangler secret for staging\\n2. Start API locally with `wrangler dev` — verify search endpoint returns results:\\n   ```\\n   curl \\\"http://localhost:8787/api/v1/cache/entireio/cli/checkpoints/search?q=authentication&branch=main\\\"\\n   ```\\n3. Start frontend locally — type in the search box and verify:\\n   - Debounced API calls (no call until 300ms after typing stops)\\n   - Results display in the same ListView format\\n   - Empty query shows normal checkpoint list\\n   - \\\"No results\\\" state shows for queries with no matches\\n   - Loading spinner while search is in flight\\n\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1925,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":126609,\"output_tokens\":1907,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":1925,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYhUscFpSuS8GVkcMEzZP\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"5a68ec15-1e3c-4973-8c4e-1a8fb56221b7\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T05:24:06.232Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"5a68ec15-1e3c-4973-8c4e-1a8fb56221b7\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/evisdrenova/code/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"504a5988-0478-439b-bb41-a58eeaef723a\",\"version\":\"2.1.56\",\"gitBranch\":\"main\",\"slug\":\"resilient-squishing-fern\",\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"<tool_use_error>File has not been read yet. Read it first before writing to it.</tool_use_error>\",\"is_error\":true